# Design Rules

Follow these visual and UX rules strictly.

---

# Design Philosophy

Design principles:

- Minimal and modern
- Clean hierarchy
- Strong readability
- Large whitespace usage
- Subtle visual feedback
- Content first
- Consistent spacing
- Soft contrast over extreme contrast
- Focus on usability before decoration

Avoid:

- Heavy shadows
- Excessive gradients
- Multiple accent colors
- Visual clutter
- Aggressive animations
- Random spacing values

---

# Color System

Design uses:

- Warm yellow/golden primary
- Neutral grayscale foundation
- Soft semantic colors

Primary Palette:

```ts
export const PRIMARY_COLORS = {

50:"#FFF8E8",
100:"#FFF1C9",
200:"#FFE59A",
300:"#FFD65F",
400:"#F7C83D",
500:"#F4B400",
600:"#D99A00",
700:"#B67D00",
800:"#8F6100",
900:"#684500"

}
```

Neutral Palette:

```ts
export const NEUTRAL_COLORS = {

50:"#F9FAFB",
100:"#F3F4F6",
200:"#E5E7EB",
300:"#D1D5DB",
400:"#9CA3AF",
500:"#6B7280",
600:"#4B5563",
700:"#374151",
800:"#1F2937",
900:"#111827"

}
```

Semantic Palette:

```ts
export const SUCCESS="#22C55E"

export const WARNING="#F59E0B"

export const ERROR="#EF4444"

export const INFO="#3B82F6"
```

Rules:

- Yellow is the primary accent color
- Neutral colors dominate UI
- Primary color should not overwhelm layout
- Use semantic colors only for feedback states
- Never use pure black (#000000)
- Never use pure white (#FFFFFF)

Prefer:

Background:

```css
bg-neutral-50
```

Cards:

```css
bg-white
border-neutral-200
```

Primary action:

```css
bg-primary-500
```

---

# Typography

Primary font:

```css
Inter Tight
```

Fallback:

```css
font-family:
'Inter Tight',
'Inter',
sans-serif;
```

Rules:

- Use one primary font family
- Maintain strong hierarchy
- Prefer font weight over color differences

Typography scale:

```ts
Display:
text-5xl
font-bold

Heading1:
text-4xl
font-semibold

Heading2:
text-3xl
font-semibold

Heading3:
text-2xl
font-medium

Body:
text-base
font-normal

Caption:
text-sm
font-normal
```

Avoid:

- Excessive font sizes
- Multiple font families
- Decorative fonts

---

# Spacing System

Use 8px spacing system.

Scale:

```ts
1 = 4px
2 = 8px
3 = 12px
4 = 16px
5 = 20px
6 = 24px
8 = 32px
10 = 40px
12 = 48px
16 = 64px
20 = 80px
```

Rules:

- Maintain consistent spacing
- Avoid arbitrary values
- Prefer Tailwind spacing scale

Avoid:

```tsx
className="mt-[13px]"
```

Prefer:

```tsx
className="mt-4"
```

---

# Border Radius

Use soft rounded corners.

Scale:

```ts
small:
rounded-md

medium:
rounded-xl

large:
rounded-2xl
```

Rules:

- Inputs: rounded-xl
- Cards: rounded-2xl
- Buttons: rounded-xl
- Dialogs: rounded-2xl

Avoid:

```tsx
rounded-full
```

unless intentionally needed

---

# Shadows

Prefer subtle shadows.

Use:

```tsx
shadow-sm

shadow-md
```

Avoid:

```tsx
shadow-2xl
```

Rules:

- Use shadow only for hierarchy
- Never use shadows for decoration

---

# Buttons

Rules:

Primary:

```tsx
bg-primary-500
text-neutral-900
```

Secondary:

```tsx
bg-neutral-100
text-neutral-800
```

Ghost:

```tsx
hover:bg-neutral-100
```

Button behavior:

- Loading states required
- Disabled states required
- Hover feedback required
- Focus states required

---

# Forms

Rules:

- Labels always visible
- Errors below field
- Required fields indicated
- Use helper text when needed
- Use validation feedback

Avoid placeholders replacing labels

Bad:

```tsx
<Input placeholder="Email"/>
```

Good:

```tsx
<Label>Email</Label>
<Input/>
```

---

# Cards

Rules:

- Rounded corners
- Soft border
- Internal spacing
- Clear content hierarchy

Prefer:

```tsx
<Card className='rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 p-6'>
```

---

# Motion

Rules:

- Use subtle transitions only
- Duration:

150ms–300ms

Use:

```tsx
transition-all
duration-200
```

Avoid:

- Bounce animations
- Infinite animations
- Large transforms

---

# Accessibility

Always:

- Maintain contrast ratio
- Keyboard navigation
- Visible focus state
- Semantic HTML
- ARIA attributes where needed

---

# Responsive Rules

Design mobile first.

Breakpoints:

```ts
sm:640px
md:768px
lg:1024px
xl:1280px
2xl:1536px
```

Rules:

- Stack content on mobile
- Avoid horizontal scrolling
- Prefer flexible layouts

---

# Component Behavior

Components must:

- Have loading states
- Have empty states
- Have error states
- Support accessibility
- Respect design tokens